<h1 class="homeTitle">3D Assets Management System</h1>
<p class="authors">Authors: Ethan Hong &amp; Anthony Sokry</p>
<div>
    <p class="description">Simple system for managing static 3D models, materials, textures, and accompanying artists.</p>
    <div class="homeTables">
        <div class="tabelCard">
            <h1>Models</h1>
            <p>Manage records of static 3D models.</p>
