        </div>
        <div class="tabelCard">
            <h1>Artists</h1>
            <p>Manage records of individual artists.</p>
            <a href="/artists">&#10141; VIEW</a>
        </div>
        <div class="tabelCard">
            <h1>Materials</h1>
            <p>Manage records of materials made by artists.</p>
            <a href="/materials">&#10141; VIEW</a>
        </div>
        <div class="tabelCard">
            <h1>Textures</h1>
            <p>Manage records of textures made by artists.</p>
            <a href="/textures">&#10141; VIEW</a>
        </div>
